{"tid":1072434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix動畫《愛．死．機械人》 香港取景　內容涉英殖香港","createTime":"2019-03-22T04:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T15:57:11.000Z","uid":47714,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b435e301c26bd995bfb6c3fb9f2c0ed6453c5ac1","tid":1072434,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/netflix動畫-愛-死-機械人-香港取景-內容涉英殖香港/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2Fnetflix%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB-%E6%84%9B-%E6%AD%BB-%E6%A9%9F%E6%A2%B0%E4%BA%BA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%96%E6%99%AF-%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E6%B6%89%E8%8B%B1%E6%AE%96%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroEz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=db8057ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2Fnetflix%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB-%E6%84%9B-%E6%AD%BB-%E6%A9%9F%E6%A2%B0%E4%BA%BA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%96%E6%99%AF-%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E6%B6%89%E8%8B%B1%E6%AE%96%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F&h=9e32d59f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/netflix動畫-愛-死-機械人-香港取景-內容涉英殖香港/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/54381480_10157410150409924_6547592791378100224_o_hjoVR_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F54381480_10157410150409924_6547592791378100224_o_hjoVR_1200x0.png&h=dd0e8266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國影視串流平台 Netflix 18 禁動畫影集《愛．死．機械人》上架不到一星期，已大獲好評。《愛．死．機械人》第一季共 18 集，每集都是獨立故事，題材多元。其中第三集《目擊者（The Witness）》以及第八集《祝你順利（Good Hunting）》均與香港有關，前者出現了大量香港街景，後者則以英殖香港為故事背景。<br />\n<br />\n《愛．死．機械人》由 Joshua Donen、David Fincher、Jennifer Miller、Tim Miller 共同製作，每集都由不同導演、動畫公司負責，風格各異，集科幻、cyberpunk 元素於一身。故事題材亦非常豐富，包括種族歧視、威權政治、人性等。單集時長則從 5 到 15 分鐘不等。<br />\n<br />\n其中第三集《目擊者》讓香港觀眾眼前一亮，因影片中出現了大量熟悉的香港場景，包括唐樓、霓虹燈、屏風樓、紅的等等。更有網友找出與《目擊者》相應的香港實景，包括黃埔花園、鰂魚涌海山樓、大角咀中美樓、尖沙咀美麗都大廈、旺角後巷等。故事講述女主角目擊一宗謀殺案，但被兇手發現後，隨即在香港大街小巷上演一場「貓捉老鼠」的追逐戲碼。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E38081_dDyJz_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE38081_dDyJz_1200x0.jpg&h=bf1b1cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.43.35_meitu_3_QERUq_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.43.35_meitu_3_QERUq_1200x0.jpg&h=282765ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/54416664_10157410146854924_8612366561941913600_o_AoJBN_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F54416664_10157410146854924_8612366561941913600_o_AoJBN_1200x0.jpg&h=585cc104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.45.09_meitu_7_s5p9Y_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.45.09_meitu_7_s5p9Y_1200x0.jpg&h=766a1e87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.43.08_meitu_2_e88ih_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.43.08_meitu_2_e88ih_1200x0.jpg&h=aa67307c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/54522651_10157410149799924_2974623903156011008_o_ceeGU_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F54522651_10157410149799924_2974623903156011008_o_ceeGU_1200x0.jpg&h=5758ef4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/53908280_10157410149524924_4563577535694110720_o_7KihU_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F53908280_10157410149524924_4563577535694110720_o_7KihU_1200x0.jpg&h=9f3064d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.43.24_meitu_6_BqkYf_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.43.24_meitu_6_BqkYf_1200x0.jpg&h=123f3aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88BE58D8812.46.33_FFSy1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88BE58D8812.46.33_FFSy1_1200x0.png&h=3cb6ee7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了《目擊者》外，第八集《祝你順利（Good Hunting）》同樣與香港有關，故事背景涉及英殖時期的香港，講述一名鬼魂獵人的兒子與狐狸精之間的友情。《祝你順利（Good Hunting）》改編自美籍華裔科幻作家劉宇昆的同名短篇小說《Good Hunting》。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.49.30_meitu_1_Wr1my_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.49.30_meitu_1_Wr1my_1200x0.jpg&h=41b11999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.49.35_meitu_2_cHJGC_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.49.35_meitu_2_cHJGC_1200x0.jpg&h=2a12862b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.49.38_meitu_3_4R4y7_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.49.38_meitu_3_4R4y7_1200x0.jpg&h=7f05847e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.50.35_meitu_4_4rBfZ_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-03-1920E4B88AE58D8811.50.35_meitu_4_4rBfZ_1200x0.jpg&h=e050727c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Good-Hunting-Love-Death-and-Robots_V9Meo_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FGood-Hunting-Love-Death-and-Robots_V9Meo_1200x0.jpg&h=1b245bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片為 Netflix 截圖）"},{"pid":"a66283e64fa24047dbb94252a6837df40c6b5c4d","tid":1072434,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"華麗留名"},{"pid":"28ed51235beac6e26f2d228bb78741e4bd57bf49","tid":1072434,"uid":67655,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"畫面好靚"},{"pid":"e3d406c507c5d5e2814723bfc2ac0a80ecaef915","tid":1072434,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"8befc8c23044e1bae4a83d14b3f4d5755054bc52","tid":1072434,"uid":209487,"like":2,"dislike":73,"score":-71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:21:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9d95edd13751472d1b28769132fc20b31d1109d","tid":1072434,"uid":57297,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"8befc8c23044e1bae4a83d14b3f4d5755054bc52